                        <center><h1><span id="cph_lbl_title">Infiniti Design 2008 G37 Sedan Concept at SEMA in Las Vegas, Nevada</span></h1></center>
                                        
                        <table class="style1">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="style2">
                                        <iframe src="//www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.knfilters.com%2Fnews%2Fnews.aspx%3Fid%3D1680&amp;send=false&amp;layout=standard&amp;width=450&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font&amp;height=35" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:250px; height:35px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
                                        </td>
                                <td>
                                    <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-hashtags="knfilters" data-dnt="true">Tweet</a><script>!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],p=/^http:/.test(d.location)?'http':'https';if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src=p+'://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js';fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document, 'script', 'twitter-wjs');</script>
						            </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                            
                           
							<span id="cph_lbl_release_text"><font size="2">
Manny de Encio of Automotive Design Concepts in Huntington Beach, California has built custom cars for more than twenty-five years. When he was younger he worked at his familys Porsche and Mercedes Benz shop.<br>
<br>

<DIV style="float: left; width: 250px; height: 523px; padding-right: 8px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 4px">

<CENTER style="width: 250px; height: 513px">

<font size="2">

<a href="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc1.jpg">
<img border="0" src="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc1s.jpg" width="250" height="252" alt="Infiniti concept car designed for use on the Autobahn along with The Las Vegas Strip"></a></font><BR>


<font size="1">
Infiniti concept car designed for use on the Autobahn along with The Las Vegas Strip</font><br>
<br>


<font size="2">


<a href="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc3.jpg">
<img border="0" src="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc3s.jpg" width="250" height="185" alt="Manny de Encio of Automotive Design Concepts transported Infiniti from Huntington Beach, California to SEMA show in Las Vegas, Nevada"></a></font><BR>



<font size="1">Manny de Encio of Automotive Design Concepts transported Infiniti from Huntington Beach, California to SEMA show in Las Vegas, Nevada</font><br>

</CENTER>



</DIV>I like the constant change and the options of so many different designs, said De Encio. There are so many ways to express yourself when you customize a vehicle. One of his designs was the star of the Infiniti booth at SEMA (Specialty Equipment Market Association) at the Las Vegas Convention Center in Nevada.<br>
<DIV style="float: right; width: 250px; height: 442px; padding-left: 8px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 4px">

<CENTER>

<font size="2">

<a href="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc2.jpg">
<img border="0" src="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc2s.jpg" width="250" height="165" alt="K&N air intake system 69-7082TS on modified Infiniti 2008 G37 Sedan Concept"></a></font><BR>


<font size="1">

K&N air intake system 69-7082TS on modified Infiniti 2008 G37 Sedan Concept</font><br>
<br>




<a href="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc4.jpg">
<img border="0" src="http://www.knfilters.com/images/press/adc4s.jpg" width="250" height="212" alt="2008 G37 Sedan Concept was painted with base gold under eleven coats of Sunset Red Candy"></a><BR>




<font size="1">

2008 G37 Sedan Concept was painted with base gold under eleven coats of Sunset Red Candy</font></CENTER>



</DIV><br>
We call it the G37 Sedan Concept, said De Encio. Our design was European, inside and out. Our G37 Sedan is equally ready for the Autobahn as it is for a night on the Las Vegas Strip. Automotive Design Concepts extended the fenders for more than 2.5 inches for a wide body approach. The paint job, however, really stood out, said De Encio. Its from PPG Industries Vibrance Collection Radiance line. We put eleven coats of Sunset Red Candy 
paint on top of a gold base.
<br>
<br>
K&N supplied De Encio with its 
<a href="http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-7082TS">69-7082TS</a> air intake system. K&N, hands down, makes the best air intake kit on the market today, he said. K&N sees the fit and enhances the way vehicles perform. We noticed the increase in horsepower immediately. We also equipped our car with a K&N oil filter.<br>
<br>
Other modifications are:<br>
<br>
ADVENT HR7008 7 Touch Panel Mobile Video Headrest System with Dual Integrated Top Load DVD Players and Game Controllers<br>
AUTOMOTIVE DESIGN CONCEPTS  Custom Suede Seat Inserts Suede Headliner, Visors, Pillars and Door Panel Inserts<br>
AUTO EXPLOSION  2 Custom Wide Body and Candy Paint<br>
BLACK FLYS Driving Glasses<br>
GENUINE INFINITI PARTS  - M35 Door Handles<br>
K&N FILTERS - 
<a href="http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-7082TS">69-7082TS</a> Air Intake System and Performance Gold Oil Filter<br>	
KINETIK AUDIO  HC 1400 Power Cell<br>
LEXANI  LSS 10 Black and Machine Finish with Stainless Lip 20x8.5 and 20x10 Wheels and Lexani Premium Edition Upper and Bumper Grilles<br>
LICENSE FRAME INC.  Custom License Frame and Chrome Plated Emblem<br>  
MAGNAFLOW PERFORMANCE EXHAUST  Dual 2.5 Stainless Cat Back Exhaust System with 4 Round Double Walled Tips<br>
MEGUIARS  NXT Generation Car Care Products<br>
METRA ELECTRONICS  Tsunami Audio Installation Kits and Accessories<br>
MOTORSPORT TECHNOLOGY  Hub Centric Wheel Spacers<br>	
PPG INDUSTRIES  Vibrance Collection Radiance II Sunset Red Candy Paint<br>
POLK AUDIO  Mobile Monitor Series Speakers and Amplifiers<br>
ROAD MAGNET PERFORMANCE SPRINGS  1.75 Performance Springs<br>
STILLEN  Stillen Sports Cross Drilled Rotors and Metal Matrix Brake Pads<br>
SUPERIOR MATS  Custom Embroidered Floor Mat Set<br>
TOYO TIRES  Proxes 4 - 245/35ZR20 and 295/30ZR20 Tires
<br>
<br>
De Encio said it was another great year at SEMA and wanted to thank Infiniti as well as all his other partners for bringing his concept to reality.
<br>
<br>Find K&amp;N products for your vehicle using the <a href="http://www.knfilters.com/search/appsearch.aspx">K&amp;N application search</a> then use the <a href="http://www.knfilters.com/search/dealersearch.aspx">K&amp;N dealer search</a> to find a K&amp;N dealer in your part of the world.



</font></span>
